580
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,280
Then what?

581
00:31:13,360 --> 00:31:14,400
To tell the truth.

582
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:18,920
We actually had a misunderstanding,

583
00:31:19,440 --> 00:31:20,720
but it's gone now.

584
00:31:21,080 --> 00:31:22,040
We all admire you.

585
00:31:22,040 --> 00:31:22,600
In the future,

586
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:24,160
we will cooperate well with you.

587
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:25,280
And we also agree

588
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:28,160
that No. 2 must do better than No. 1.

589
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:31,050
Why are you saying this?

590
00:31:31,320 --> 00:31:32,000
Isn't it because

591
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:34,600
we'll be working together as partners from now on?

592
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:35,920
Well,

593
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:37,880
between partners, there should

594
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:38,840
be no secrets.

595
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,370
What on earth are you trying to say?

596
00:31:48,520 --> 00:31:50,120
Nothing much. It's just that

597
00:31:50,360 --> 00:31:51,560
we didn't know each other well before,

598
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:53,880
so it's inevitable to have some misunderstandings.

599
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:54,440
Right?

600
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:55,880
So it doesn't matter.

601
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:56,800
From now on,

602
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:57,720
to us, you are

603
00:31:57,720 --> 00:32:00,160
a brand new version, a brand new you.

604
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:01,240
We will all listen to you,

605
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:03,200
follow your commands, and obey your arrangements.

606
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:04,400
A little welcome gift.

607
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:07,000
Please advise and take care of us in the future.

608
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:09,640
Just a small token of appreciation.

609
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:10,440
It's nothing.

610
00:32:21,320 --> 00:32:22,250
What do you mean?

611
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:25,570
I'm asking you what this means.

612
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:26,640
It means

613
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:28,300
let's all work hard together.

614
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:40,440
Wu Wei.

615
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:43,720
I didn't expect that despite your poor work ability,

616
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:45,980
