620
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,280
No, no, no.

621
00:32:55,280 --> 00:32:55,920
It's a misunderstanding.

622
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:56,980
I didn't mean that.

623
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,640
Take it and leave.

624
00:32:59,120 --> 00:32:59,600
Leave.

625
00:33:00,320 --> 00:33:00,800
Don't. Calm down.

626
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:01,320
Get out.

627
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:02,480
Don't.

628
00:33:02,480 --> 00:33:03,120
Get out.

629
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:05,200
My model.

630
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:05,960
Calm down and let's talk properly.

631
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:06,640
Get out!

632
00:33:07,680 --> 00:33:08,880
Let's talk properly.

633
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:11,640
Xu Xu.

634
00:33:12,120 --> 00:33:12,720
Xu Xu.

635
00:33:13,560 --> 00:33:15,120
I didn't mean that. I...

636
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:21,650
The solar panel has been rebooted and connected.

637
00:33:22,320 --> 00:33:24,850
Turn on the backup battery unit power switch.

638
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:30,600
The battery unit power switch is on.

639
00:33:31,040 --> 00:33:32,770
Power combination completed.

640
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,570
Did you find out the reason?

641
00:33:34,800 --> 00:33:36,530
I'll check again immediately.

642
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:42,360
Report.

643
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:44,200
There is no problem with the signal.

644
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:46,330
The operation commands are also fine.

645
00:33:49,640 --> 00:33:50,920
Try sending the command again.

646
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:51,520
Yes.

647
00:34:01,920 --> 00:34:02,800
Why?

648
00:34:04,520 --> 00:34:05,920
Why is there no response?

649
00:34:07,480 --> 00:34:09,199
The operation just now was clearly compliant.

650
00:34:09,199 --> 00:34:10,530
There was no deviation.

651
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:15,000
How about we try again?

652
00:34:24,719 --> 00:34:25,400
Report.

653
00:34:26,120 --> 00:34:28,580
We can receive uplink and downlink signals,

654
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:31,360
but the commands are currently invalid.

655
00:34:36,120 --> 00:34:38,520
Everyone, gather in the conference room

656
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:40,120
and wait for further orders.

657
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:54,760
According to the preliminary judgment,

658
00:34:54,760 --> 00:34:56,690
because there is no air on the moon,

659
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:59,960
with lower gravity and strong radiation,

660
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,360
and a large temperature difference on the surface,

661
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:04,290
under the combined effect of these complex factors,

662
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:06,640
the cable insulation on the surface of the Yutu rover

663
00:35:06,640 --> 00:35:08,170
has become extremely weak.

664
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,880
During the movement of the Yutu rover,

665
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:13,880
the insulation was torn by rocks on the lunar surface.

666
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:17,690
The cables were exposed to excessively high temperatures.

667
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:21,000
Although the telemetry and control functions remain good,

668
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:24,000
subsequent operations will be highly risky.

669
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,960
Therefore, superiors have instructed that

670
00:35:25,960 --> 00:35:27,280
starting today,

671
00:35:28,120 --> 00:35:29,720
the driving mission is over.

672
00:36:11,520 --> 00:36:12,320
Tell me,

673
00:36:12,960 --> 00:36:14,420
what's the deal with Xu Xu?

674
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:17,640
What kind of beef does he have with Jade Rabbit One?

675
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:18,600
There's no beef.

676
00:36:18,600 --> 00:36:19,400
Really?

677
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:21,800
The moment I mentioned Jade Rabbit One,

678
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:22,960
he lost his temper.

679
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,920
I heard that because of Jade Rabbit,

680
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:29,560
he had a falling out with his partner.

681
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:30,520
He and his partner

682
00:36:30,520 --> 00:36:32,040
had been working together ever since they joined the center

683
00:36:32,040 --> 00:36:33,200
as a team.

684
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:34,960
And because of this,

685
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:37,810
