686
00:36:40,080 --> 00:36:41,810
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

687
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:43,880
You didn't ask me. Seriously.

688
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:46,080
Besides, it's not important.

689
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,800
I'm done.

690
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:50,200
I stepped right on the landmine.

691
00:36:50,200 --> 00:36:51,520
Right in the line of fire.

692
00:36:51,520 --> 00:36:52,400
What?

693
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:55,720
Never mind.

694
00:36:55,720 --> 00:36:57,180
You wouldn't understand.

695
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:59,340
Tell me. What wouldn't I understand?

696
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:01,340
I completely stepped on his toes.

697
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:05,880
But it's okay, Wei.

698
00:37:06,320 --> 00:37:07,400
I think

699
00:37:07,720 --> 00:37:09,520
a big shot like Xu Xu

700
00:37:09,520 --> 00:37:11,400
is strictly professional with work.

701
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,760
I guess

702
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:17,040
