703
00:37:17,040 --> 00:37:18,080
and it struck a chord.

704
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:19,080
In our line of work,

705
00:37:19,080 --> 00:37:20,000
having a partner in sync

706
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,360
is hard to come by.

707
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:24,320
Who in our center doesn't envy

708
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:25,680
