709
00:37:29,680 --> 00:37:30,880
You sure can talk.

710
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:33,130
I'm leaving. Have fun by yourself.

711
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:36,760
I'm telling the truth.

712
00:37:44,720 --> 00:37:45,360
Mr. Qin.

713
00:37:46,240 --> 00:37:46,840
Ziqi.

714
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:50,240
About the Yuetu rover's algorithm,

715
00:37:50,240 --> 00:37:51,320
