716
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:52,980
Could you give me some advice?

717
00:37:55,440 --> 00:37:56,640
Sit here.

718
00:37:56,640 --> 00:37:59,600
Have you been sleeping in the office these past few days?

719
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:01,730
That's just how it is when I'm swamped.

720
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:03,160
About the algorithm you mentioned,

721
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:06,440
I actually stayed up all night to sort out some ideas.

722
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:09,080
Take a look. It might help.

723
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:13,400
Actually, your original proposal

724
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:15,000
was already quite complete.

725
00:38:15,600 --> 00:38:16,600
Quite complete.

726
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:18,040
Obviously,

727
00:38:18,680 --> 00:38:20,760
you and Xu Xu have meshed pretty well.

728
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:22,840
Xu Xu has high requirements for the proposal.

729
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,240
Although there's pressure in communication,

730
00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:25,400
it's indeed effective.

731
00:38:25,400 --> 00:38:27,520
He takes things quite seriously.

732
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:29,400
But people who are serious

733
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:31,000
are all simple, right?

734
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:35,400
There's a lot of time pressure right now.

735
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:37,520
Since you've secured this task,

736
00:38:38,040 --> 00:38:39,520
