750
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:11,640
Lao Qin.

751
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:12,600
Dr. Xu.

752
00:39:13,160 --> 00:39:15,360
It seems I need to talk to you in private.

753
00:39:17,400 --> 00:39:18,120
Ziqi.

754
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:19,720
Wait for me at the door.

755
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:21,440
Come, step outside for a moment.

756
00:39:21,440 --> 00:39:22,100
Have a seat.

757
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:34,000
I originally wanted to wait for the expert consultation

758
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:35,360
and the surgical plan to be finalized

759
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:36,640
before notifying you to be admitted.

760
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:38,040
But the current situation

761
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:39,880
doesn't allow for any more delays.

762
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:40,880
The hospital

763
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,880
