00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:06,560
I see.

777
00:40:13,200 --> 00:40:15,640
Here, fish head with rice.

778
00:40:16,120 --> 00:40:17,580
This place makes the best.

779
00:40:18,240 --> 00:40:19,280
If we weren't so close,

780
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:21,080
