828
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:32,120
I will always be with you.

829
00:42:32,120 --> 00:42:33,720
We still have a long way to go.

830
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:35,520
We are scientists.

831
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:38,920
We study the laws of the universe.

832
00:42:39,720 --> 00:42:40,960
Birth, aging, illness, and death

833
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:42,880
